{
  "title": "Fluffy椰香沙拉",
  "description": "这是一道轻盈的中东风味菜肴，融合了松软的 shredded coconut 和酸辣腌菜，适合低卡饮食。",
  "cuisine": "中东",
  "diet": [
    "low-carb"
  ],
  "meal": "snack",
  "ingredients": [
    {
      "name": "shredded coconut",
      "amount": "1/4 cup"
    },
    {
      "name": "pickle",
      "amount": "2 pieces",
      "notes": "选用低糖或无糖的腌制蔬菜"
    },
    {
      "name": "lime juice",
      "amount": "1 tablespoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "sesame oil",
      "amount": "1 teaspoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "ginger paste",
      "amount": "1/4 teaspoon"
    },
    {
      "name": "cumin powder",
      "amount": "1/8 teaspoon"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "将 shredded coconut 和 pickle 碎成小块。",
    "在碗中，加入 shredded coconut、pickle 以及生姜泥和孜然粉。搅拌均匀。",
    "挤入几滴柠檬汁，并淋上少许芝麻油。",
    "根据口味调整咸度。",
    "拌匀后即可食用。"
  ],
